Deemos, not really helpless at all, rolls out of the way and stands up.

Deemos: You are intelligent enough not to fall for it, I see.

Deemos realizes he got his arm cut up pretty badly.

Deemos: I estimate that I could go on for another few hits.

Deemos, being as cowardly as he is, bows to Aerotaur.

Deemos: May we meet again someday, grand warrior.

Deemos runs, grabbing Rizopas' head, Doom Ice picking up his body.

Doom Ice: Tell the kid to shoot someone his own size.

Doom Ice joked around some. It was in her personality. The mini-Mafia runs
off after Deemos, Doom Ice following as well.

Shokaract: You coward, you could have taken him!

Shokaract was hoping that Deemos would have gotten killed. Serge starts off,
Diskus landing on his back...
